description.original: A plugin that turns web apps into panes using iframes with custom styling. Also comes with presets for Google Keep, Todoist and more.
description.translation: 一个使用带有自定义样式的iframe将Web应用程序转换为标签页的插件，预设了Google Keep、Todoist等。
